sentences: Jason Gilbert, known by his nickname JG , is a Caymanian record producer, songwriter, mixing engineer and DJ.
JG has produced for artists including Eminem, Bad Meets Evil, Akon, Christina Aguilera and Taio Cruz.
In 2011, Gilbert won a Grammy Award for his production work on Eminem's Recovery album.
Later in 2011, JG produced the first single off of Bad Meets Evil debut album.
The single charted at #32 on the Billboard Hot 100.
JG is the founder of Happy Parrot Records and has a Master of Science in Finance degree from Florida International University (FIU).
JG is the founder and member of DJ Group (Skorch Bun It).
